example.code: PS C:\> $results = Get-IAMServiceLastAccessedDetailWithEntity -JobId f0b7a819-eab0-929b-dc26-ca598911cb9f -ServiceNamespace ec2 PS C:\> $results Output: EntityDetailsList : {Amazon.IdentityManagement.Model.EntityDetails} Error : IsTruncated : False JobCompletionDate : 12/29/19 11:19:31 AM JobCreationDate : 12/29/19 11:19:31 AM JobStatus : COMPLETED Marker : PS C:\> $results.EntityDetailsList Output: EntityInfo LastAuthenticated ---------- ----------------- Amazon.IdentityManagement.Model.EntityInfo 11/16/19 3:47:00 PM PS C:\> $results.EntityInfo Output: Arn : arn:aws:iam::123456789012:user/TestUser Id : AIDA4NBK5CXF5TZHU1234 Name : TestUser Path : / Type : USER
example.description: This example provides the last accessed timestamp for the service in the request by that respective IAM entity.
